metadata.name: Flying Saucer Macarons - Valentine's Edition
metadata.description: It's Valentine's Day! To show my love and appreciation for all my collectors I have created a special delicious gift for you, a box of six macarons from Flying Saucer (the make the best macarons on Eupraxia!!) Three rose petal with fig filling and three strawberry with vanilla filling, nestled in a red box with the Flying Saucer logo embossed in silver. This 3D .gltf file is ready to be placed in your metaverse home and enjoyed! xoxo Marzipan
